casebody.data:
In re Resignation of Blair.

[Cite as In re Resignation of Blair (1990), 49 Ohio St. 3d 605.]

(No. 90-186 Submitted February 7, 1990 Decided February 21, 1990.)

The resignation of James C. Blair as an attorney is accepted.

Moyer, C.J., Sweeney, Holmes, Douglas, Wright, H. Brown and Resnick, JJ., concur.
